textAnnotations.description:
Iffter what seemed an undre period of repetition, the vice
went on to describe the launching of the Thetan colony
in Sussex, in all its obscene details. Then the radio
event dead again, and Steve had no stomach for
treatfuit. It was a
beautiful
tiful day, as firsts - of. Jure
should be. Here
got out the car and traversed the
same empty streets as he least the night before,
to keep ape appointment with Heathe.
